---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { TEST_COUNT, DOMAIN_COUNT, THEOREM_COUNT } from '../lib/metrics';
---

<BaseLayout title="Cognitive Equalizer — Aequator Cognitivus" description="Interactive AI evaluation tool using the GCD kernel. Score 8 channels, derive three-valued verdicts, and explore geometric slaughter — all client-side.">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <div class="mb-8 text-center">
      <div class="inline-block mb-3 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-kernel-800/60 border border-kernel-700/40 text-[10px] font-mono text-kernel-400 uppercase tracking-widest">
        Aequator Cognitivus · CE-v1-frozen · 8 Channels · 3 Verdicts
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-kernel-100 mb-3 tracking-tight">
        Cognitive Equalizer
      </h1>
      <p class="text-kernel-400 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <em class="text-amber-400/80">Non agens mensurat, sed structura.</em> — Not the agent measures, but the structure.
      </p>
      <p class="text-kernel-500 text-sm mt-2 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        A standalone module that externalises every agent-dependent decision point into frozen, verifiable structure.
        Same input + same contract → same verdict, regardless of which AI runs it.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- ═══════ The Spine ═══════ -->
    <div class="mb-6 bg-kernel-900/40 border border-kernel-700/40 rounded-xl p-5">
      <h2 class="text-xs font-bold text-purple-400/80 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">The Spine — Every Evaluation Follows This Path</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-2 text-xs font-mono mb-3">
        <span class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-kernel-800/60 rounded-lg border border-kernel-700/30 text-green-400">CONTRACT<br/><span class="text-kernel-600 text-[9px]">freeze thresholds</span></span>
        <span class="text-kernel-600">→</span>
        <span class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-kernel-800/60 rounded-lg border border-kernel-700/30 text-amber-400">CANON<br/><span class="text-kernel-600 text-[9px]">5 words</span></span>
        <span class="text-kernel-600">→</span>
        <span class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-kernel-800/60 rounded-lg border border-kernel-700/30 text-cyan-400">CLOSURES<br/><span class="text-kernel-600 text-[9px]">regime gates</span></span>
        <span class="text-kernel-600">→</span>
        <span class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-kernel-800/60 rounded-lg border border-kernel-700/30 text-purple-400">LEDGER<br/><span class="text-kernel-600 text-[9px]">debit/credit</span></span>
        <span class="text-kernel-600">→</span>
        <span class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-kernel-800/60 rounded-lg border border-kernel-700/30 text-red-400">STANCE<br/><span class="text-kernel-600 text-[9px]">verdict</span></span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-center text-[10px] text-kernel-600 italic">Omnia per spinam transeunt — Everything passes through the spine</p>
    </div>

    <!-- ═══════ Five Decision Points ═══════ -->
    <div class="mb-6 bg-kernel-900/50 border border-kernel-700/50 rounded-xl p-5">
      <h2 class="text-sm font-bold text-amber-400/80 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Five Externalized Decision Points</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-5 gap-3 text-xs">
        <div class="bg-kernel-800/50 rounded-lg p-3 border border-kernel-700/30">
          <div class="text-green-400 font-bold mb-1">1. Thresholds</div>
          <div class="text-kernel-500">Frozen — seam-derived, not chosen. ε=10⁻⁸, p=3, α=1.0, tol=0.005</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-kernel-800/50 rounded-lg p-3 border border-kernel-700/30">
          <div class="text-amber-400 font-bold mb-1">2. Vocabulary</div>
          <div class="text-kernel-500">Five words only: Drift · Fidelity · Roughness · Return · Integrity</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-kernel-800/50 rounded-lg p-3 border border-kernel-700/30">
          <div class="text-cyan-400 font-bold mb-1">3. Conclusions</div>
          <div class="text-kernel-500">Three-valued: CONFORMANT / NONCONFORMANT / NON_EVALUABLE</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-kernel-800/50 rounded-lg p-3 border border-kernel-700/30">
          <div class="text-purple-400 font-bold mb-1">4. Methodology</div>
          <div class="text-kernel-500">The Spine: Contract → Canon → Closures → Ledger → Stance</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-kernel-800/50 rounded-lg p-3 border border-kernel-700/30">
          <div class="text-red-400 font-bold mb-1">5. Ambiguity</div>
          <div class="text-kernel-500">NON_EVALUABLE — declared, never guessed away. Tertia via semper patet.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ═══════ TABS ═══════ -->
    <div class="mb-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2 border-b border-kernel-800/50 pb-3" id="ce-tabs">
      <button data-tab="interactive" class="ce-tab active px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition-all bg-amber-500/20 text-amber-400 border border-amber-500/30">
        Interactive Evaluator
      </button>
      <button data-tab="presets" class="ce-tab px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition-all text-kernel-500 hover:text-kernel-300 border border-transparent hover:border-kernel-700/30">
        Preset Demos
      </button>
      <button data-tab="channels" class="ce-tab px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition-all text-kernel-500 hover:text-kernel-300 border border-transparent hover:border-kernel-700/30">
        Channel Reference
      </button>
      <button data-tab="prompt" class="ce-tab px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition-all text-kernel-500 hover:text-kernel-300 border border-transparent hover:border-kernel-700/30">
        AI System Prompt
      </button>
      <button data-tab="download" class="ce-tab px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition-all text-kernel-500 hover:text-kernel-300 border border-transparent hover:border-kernel-700/30">
        Download & Implement
      </button>
    </div>

    <!-- ═══════ TAB: Interactive Evaluator ═══════ -->
    <div id="tab-interactive" class="ce-panel">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <!-- Left: Channel Sliders -->
        <div class="bg-kernel-900/50 border border-kernel-700/50 rounded-xl p-5">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-green-400/80 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">8 Evaluation Channels</h3>
          <div class="space-y-4" id="channel-sliders">
            <!-- Sliders generated by JS -->
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <button id="btn-evaluate" class="px-4 py-2 bg-amber-500 hover:bg-amber-400 text-kernel-950 rounded-lg text-sm font-bold transition-colors">
              Run CE Spine
            </button>
            <button id="btn-reset" class="px-3 py-2 bg-kernel-800 hover:bg-kernel-700 text-kernel-300 rounded-lg text-xs transition-colors">
              Reset All
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: Results -->
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <!-- Verdict Badge -->
          <div id="verdict-display" class="bg-kernel-900/50 border border-kernel-700/50 rounded-xl p-5 text-center">
            <div class="text-kernel-600 text-sm mb-2">Stance (Verdict)</div>
            <div id="verdict-badge" class="inline-block px-6 py-3 rounded-xl text-2xl font-black tracking-wider border-2 border-kernel-700 text-kernel-600">
              —
            </div>
            <div id="regime-badge" class="mt-2 text-xs text-kernel-500 font-mono">
              Regime: — · Critical: —
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Radar Chart (Canvas) -->
          <div class="bg-kernel-900/50 border border-kernel-700/50 rounded-xl p-5">
            <h3 class="text-xs font-bold text-cyan-400/80 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Channel Radar</h3>
            <canvas id="radar-canvas" width="320" height="320" class="mx-auto"></canvas>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Full Spine Report -->
      <div id="spine-report" class="mt-6 bg-kernel-950 border border-kernel-700/50 rounded-xl p-5 hidden">
        <h3 class="text-xs font-bold text-purple-400/80 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Full Spine Report</h3>
        <pre id="report-text" class="text-xs text-kernel-300 font-mono whitespace-pre-wrap leading-relaxed"></pre>
      </div>

      <!-- Kernel Invariants -->
      <div id="invariants-panel" class="mt-4 hidden">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-7 gap-3">
          <div class="inv-card bg-kernel-900/50 border border-kernel-700/30 rounded-lg p-3 text-center">
            <div class="text-[10px] text-kernel-600 uppercase tracking-wider">Fidelity</div>
            <div id="inv-F" class="text-lg font-bold text-green-400 font-mono">—</div>
          </div>
          <div class="inv-card bg-kernel-900/50 border border-kernel-700/30 rounded-lg p-3 text-center">
            <div class="text-[10px] text-kernel-600 uppercase tracking-wider">Drift ω</div>
            <div id="inv-omega" class="text-lg font-bold text-amber-400 font-mono">—</div>
          </div>
          <div class="inv-card bg-kernel-900/50 border border-kernel-700/30 rounded-lg p-3 text-center">
            <div class="text-[10px] text-kernel-600 uppercase tracking-wider">Entropy S</div>
            <div id="inv-S" class="text-lg font-bold text-cyan-400 font-mono">—</div>
          </div>
          <div class="inv-card bg-kernel-900/50 border border-kernel-700/30 rounded-lg p-3 text-center">
            <div class="text-[10px] text-kernel-600 uppercase tracking-wider">Curvature C</div>
            <div id="inv-C" class="text-lg font-bold text-purple-400 font-mono">—</div>
          </div>
          <div class="inv-card bg-kernel-900/50 border border-kernel-700/30 rounded-lg p-3 text-center">
            <div class="text-[10px] text-kernel-600 uppercase tracking-wider">κ</div>
            <div id="inv-kappa" class="text-lg font-bold text-kernel-300 font-mono">—</div>
          </div>
          <div class="inv-card bg-kernel-900/50 border border-kernel-700/30 rounded-lg p-3 text-center">
            <div class="text-[10px] text-kernel-600 uppercase tracking-wider">IC</div>
            <div id="inv-IC" class="text-lg font-bold text-red-400 font-mono">—</div>
          </div>
          <div class="inv-card bg-kernel-900/50 border border-kernel-700/30 rounded-lg p-3 text-center">
            <div class="text-[10px] text-kernel-600 uppercase tracking-wider">Gap Δ</div>
            <div id="inv-delta" class="text-lg font-bold text-kernel-400 font-mono">—</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ═══════ TAB: Presets ═══════ -->
    <div id="tab-presets" class="ce-panel hidden">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4" id="preset-grid">
        <!-- Populated by JS -->
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ═══════ TAB: Channel Reference ═══════ -->
    <div id="tab-channels" class="ce-panel hidden">
      <div class="bg-kernel-900/50 border border-kernel-700/50 rounded-xl p-5">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-cyan-400/80 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Eight Evaluation Channels</h3>
        <p class="text-kernel-500 text-sm mb-4">
          Each channel is scored ∈ [0.0, 1.0]. Equal weights w<sub>i</sub> = 1/8.
          The kernel computes <span class="font-mono text-green-400">F</span> (arithmetic mean) and
          <span class="font-mono text-red-400">IC</span> (geometric mean) from these 8 scores.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-3" id="channel-reference">
          <!-- Populated by JS -->
        </div>

        <div class="mt-6 bg-kernel-800/60 rounded-lg p-4 border border-amber-500/20">
          <h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-amber-400 mb-2">Geometric Slaughter Warning</h4>
          <p class="text-kernel-400 text-xs leading-relaxed">
            If <strong>any single channel</strong> drops below 0.3, the geometric mean (IC) collapses regardless
            of how strong the other 7 channels are. Example: 7 channels at 0.95 + 1 channel at 0.001 →
            <span class="font-mono text-green-400">F ≈ 0.83</span> (looks fine) but
            <span class="font-mono text-red-400">IC ≈ 0.001</span> (obliterated).
            The heterogeneity gap <span class="font-mono text-amber-400">Δ = F − IC ≈ 0.83</span> reveals the structural collapse
            that the average masks. This is the <em class="text-kernel-300">trucidatio geometrica</em>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ═══════ TAB: AI System Prompt ═══════ -->
    <div id="tab-prompt" class="ce-panel hidden">
      <div class="bg-kernel-900/50 border border-kernel-700/50 rounded-xl p-5">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-purple-400/80 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">CE System Prompt</h3>
        <p class="text-kernel-500 text-xs mb-4">
          Copy this prompt into any AI system (ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, etc.) to enable Cognitive Equalizer mode.
          The AI will then self-audit using the 8-channel Spine protocol with frozen thresholds and three-valued verdicts.
        </p>
        <div class="relative">
          <button id="btn-copy-prompt" class="absolute top-2 right-2 px-3 py-1 bg-kernel-700 hover:bg-kernel-600 text-kernel-300 rounded text-xs transition-colors z-10">
            Copy
          </button>
          <pre id="prompt-text" class="bg-kernel-950 border border-kernel-800 rounded-lg p-4 text-xs text-kernel-400 font-mono whitespace-pre-wrap leading-relaxed max-h-[600px] overflow-y-auto"></pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ═══════ TAB: Download & Implement ═══════ -->
    <div id="tab-download" class="ce-panel hidden">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <!-- Overview -->
        <div class="bg-kernel-900/50 border border-kernel-700/50 rounded-xl p-5">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-amber-400/80 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Implement the Cognitive Equalizer</h3>
          <p class="text-kernel-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
            The CE is a <strong class="text-kernel-200">standalone, zero-dependency module</strong> that can be embedded in any system.
            Three implementations are available — each produces <strong class="text-kernel-200">identical results</strong>
            because the contract is frozen: <em class="text-amber-400/80">trans suturam congelatum</em>.
          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
            <div class="bg-kernel-800/60 rounded-lg p-4 border border-green-500/20">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                <span class="text-green-400 text-lg">🐍</span>
                <span class="text-green-400 font-bold text-sm">Python</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-kernel-500 text-xs mb-3">Full implementation with CLI, system prompt, Latin aliases. Part of the UMCP package.</p>
              <code class="text-[10px] text-kernel-400 block bg-kernel-900 rounded p-2 mb-2">pip install umcp</code>
              <code class="text-[10px] text-kernel-400 block bg-kernel-900 rounded p-2">from umcp.cognitive_equalizer import CognitiveEqualizer</code>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-kernel-800/60 rounded-lg p-4 border border-cyan-500/20">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                <span class="text-cyan-400 text-lg">📘</span>
                <span class="text-cyan-400 font-bold text-sm">TypeScript</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-kernel-500 text-xs mb-3">Browser-ready module. Same formulas, same frozen parameters, same verdicts. Zero dependencies.</p>
              <code class="text-[10px] text-kernel-400 block bg-kernel-900 rounded p-2">import &lcub; engage &rcub; from './cognitive-equalizer'</code>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-kernel-800/60 rounded-lg p-4 border border-purple-500/20">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                <span class="text-purple-400 text-lg">📋</span>
                <span class="text-purple-400 font-bold text-sm">System Prompt</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-kernel-500 text-xs mb-3">Paste into any AI chat to enable CE mode. No code required — the AI becomes the evaluator.</p>
              <button id="btn-copy-prompt-dl" class="px-3 py-1 bg-purple-500/20 hover:bg-purple-500/30 text-purple-400 rounded text-xs transition-colors border border-purple-500/30">
                Copy Prompt
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Download Links -->
        <div class="bg-kernel-900/50 border border-kernel-700/50 rounded-xl p-5">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-green-400/80 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Download Source Files</h3>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <a id="dl-python" href="#" class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-kernel-800/60 hover:bg-kernel-700/60 rounded-lg p-4 border border-kernel-700/30 transition-colors group no-underline">
              <span class="text-2xl">🐍</span>
              <div>
                <div class="text-kernel-200 font-bold text-sm group-hover:text-green-400 transition-colors">cognitive_equalizer.py</div>
                <div class="text-kernel-500 text-xs">Complete Python implementation — 930 lines, standalone, CLI, system prompt, Latin aliases</div>
              </div>
              <span class="ml-auto text-kernel-600 text-xs">↓ .py</span>
            </a>
            <a id="dl-typescript" href="#" class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-kernel-800/60 hover:bg-kernel-700/60 rounded-lg p-4 border border-kernel-700/30 transition-colors group no-underline">
              <span class="text-2xl">📘</span>
              <div>
                <div class="text-kernel-200 font-bold text-sm group-hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors">cognitive-equalizer.ts</div>
                <div class="text-kernel-500 text-xs">TypeScript module — browser-ready, same kernel, presets, formatting utilities</div>
              </div>
              <span class="ml-auto text-kernel-600 text-xs">↓ .ts</span>
            </a>
            <a id="dl-prompt" href="#" class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-kernel-800/60 hover:bg-kernel-700/60 rounded-lg p-4 border border-kernel-700/30 transition-colors group no-underline">
              <span class="text-2xl">📋</span>
              <div>
                <div class="text-kernel-200 font-bold text-sm group-hover:text-purple-400 transition-colors">ce-system-prompt.txt</div>
                <div class="text-kernel-500 text-xs">Standalone system prompt — paste into any AI to enable CE mode</div>
              </div>
              <span class="ml-auto text-kernel-600 text-xs">↓ .txt</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Architecture -->
        <div class="bg-kernel-900/50 border border-kernel-700/50 rounded-xl p-5">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-purple-400/80 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Architecture Overview</h3>
          <pre class="text-xs text-kernel-400 font-mono bg-kernel-950 rounded-lg p-4 overflow-x-auto leading-relaxed">{`┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                   COGNITIVE EQUALIZER                       │
│            Aequator Cognitivus — CE-v1-frozen               │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│                                                             │
│  INPUT: 8 Channels ∈ [0, 1]                                │
│  ┌─────────┬──────────┬──────────────┬─────────────┐       │
│  │Relevance│ Accuracy │ Completeness │ Consistency │       │
│  ├─────────┼──────────┼──────────────┼─────────────┤       │
│  │Traceab. │ Grounded │ Constraint   │ Return Fid. │       │
│  └────┬────┴────┬─────┴──────┬───────┴──────┬──────┘       │
│       │         │            │              │               │
│       ▼         ▼            ▼              ▼               │
│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────┐      │
│  │  TIER-1 KERNEL  (same formulas as Python + C)    │      │
│  │  F = Σ wᵢcᵢ    κ = Σ wᵢ ln(cᵢ,ε)              │      │
│  │  S = −Σ wᵢ h(cᵢ)   C = σ(c)/0.5               │      │
│  │  ω = 1−F       IC = exp(κ)      Δ = F−IC        │      │
│  └─────────────────────┬────────────────────────────┘      │
│                        │                                    │
│       ┌────────────────┼────────────────┐                  │
│       ▼                ▼                ▼                   │
│  ┌─────────┐   ┌──────────────┐  ┌───────────┐            │
│  │ REGIME  │   │    LEDGER    │  │   CANON   │            │
│  │ GATES   │   │  D_ω = Γ(ω) │  │ 5 Words:  │            │
│  │ Stable  │   │  D_C = α·C  │  │ Drift     │            │
│  │ Watch   │   │  Δκ balance  │  │ Fidelity  │            │
│  │ Collapse│   │  ≤ tol_seam  │  │ Roughness │            │
│  └────┬────┘   └──────┬───────┘  │ Return    │            │
│       │               │          │ Integrity │            │
│       ▼               ▼          └───────────┘            │
│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────┐      │
│  │  VERDICT (three-valued — never boolean)          │      │
│  │  CONFORMANT · NONCONFORMANT · NON_EVALUABLE      │      │
│  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────┘      │
│                                                             │
│  Frozen: ε=1e-8  p=3  α=1.0  tol=0.005                    │
│  Trans suturam congelatum — same rules both sides.         │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘`}</pre>
        </div>

        <!-- Integration Examples -->
        <div class="bg-kernel-900/50 border border-kernel-700/50 rounded-xl p-5">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-cyan-400/80 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Integration Examples</h3>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-green-400 mb-2">Python — Score an AI response</h4>
              <pre class="text-xs text-kernel-400 font-mono bg-kernel-950 rounded-lg p-3 overflow-x-auto">{`from umcp.cognitive_equalizer import CognitiveEqualizer, CEChannels

ce = CognitiveEqualizer()
channels = CEChannels(
    relevance=0.90, accuracy=0.85, completeness=0.80,
    consistency=0.95, traceability=0.70, groundedness=0.88,
    constraint_respect=0.92, return_fidelity=0.75,
)
report = ce.engage("Explain entropy", channels)
print(report.stance)           # CONFORMANT / NONCONFORMANT / NON_EVALUABLE
print(report.full_report())    # Full Spine report`}</pre>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-cyan-400 mb-2">TypeScript — Browser evaluation</h4>
              <pre class="text-xs text-kernel-400 font-mono bg-kernel-950 rounded-lg p-3 overflow-x-auto">{`import { engage, formatReport } from './cognitive-equalizer';

const report = engage({
  relevance: 0.90, accuracy: 0.85, completeness: 0.80,
  consistency: 0.95, traceability: 0.70, groundedness: 0.88,
  constraintRespect: 0.92, returnFidelity: 0.75,
});
console.log(report.stance);      // 'CONFORMANT'
console.log(formatReport(report)); // Full text report`}</pre>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-purple-400 mb-2">CLI — Command line</h4>
              <pre class="text-xs text-kernel-400 font-mono bg-kernel-950 rounded-lg p-3 overflow-x-auto">{`# Score 8 channels directly
umcp-ce --channels 0.90,0.85,0.80,0.95,0.70,0.88,0.92,0.75

# Run built-in demo
umcp-ce --demo

# Print system prompt for embedding
umcp-ce --prompt

# Latin alias works too:
aequator-cognitivus --demo`}</pre>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
         BELOW-FOLD DEEP CONTENT — scrollable sections after tabs
